name: SolDex
description: SolDex, short for Solana Decentralized Exchange, is a cutting-edge platform built on the Solana blockchain, designed to empower users with seamless, secure, and lightning-fast trading experiences. At SolDex, we're ushering in a new era of decentralized finance (DeFi) by providing a robust and user-friendly exchange ecosystem that operates with unparalleled efficiency.
